locations.title: 2x Exquisite Chest + 1 Precious Chest
locations.description:
Solve the sudoku cube puzzle. Use the journal on the ground to assign the cubes their values based on type and direction they are facing. Second time back puzzle changes slightly.

**Solution:** Each of the stones has a point-value, based on: 
- Orientation: North +1, East +2, South +3, West +4 
- Has a slate on top: +4 
- The empty field has value 9 

The goal is to have all of them sum up to the same value on horizontal, vertical and diagonal (just like Sudoku). 

So the puzzle is: 1-4 3 8 9 5-8 1 2 5-8 5-8 

The common possible sum is 15, so the solution is 4 3 8 9 5 1 2 7 6

locations.title: Luxurious Chest
locations.description:
Pressure plate puzzle. Solving the puzzle will spawn this chest, which contains a piece of [Crimson Agate](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62368).


Each of the eight pressure plates represents one of two symbols; four plates for one symbol, four plates for the other.
These symbols will appear on the nearby ruined wall when the pressure plates are activated.

Activate all four plates of one symbol before activating the other four.
The puzzle will reset whenever the other symbol is activated before a set of four is completed.


One of the pressure plates will be under a piece of Ancient Rime initially.

Activating the prompt will spawn this Luxurious Chest containing a piece of [Crimson Agate](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=63014).


Unlocks "Prodigal Son's Return" Achievement.

locations.title: Warming Seelie
locations.description:
One of a pair of Warming Seelies that must be timed together to light up all four heating torches around the icy sheet.
This one moves counter-clockwise, [the other one](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62492) counter-clockwise.
If timed well, all torches will be lit and the icy sheet will break, revealing the area below.

After the icy sheet has been broken, it will join the other two in the area below, where you must once again time the activation of the Warming Seelies to activate all heating torches at once.
This will activate the Ruin Grader, which must be defeated to gain access to the reward.

Together with the other two Seelie it rewards an [Exquisite](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62586), a [Precious](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62584) and a [Luxurious Chest](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62585).

Together with the other two Seelie it rewards an [Exquisite](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62586), a [Precious](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62584) and a [Luxurious Chest](https://mapgenie.io/genshin-impact/maps/teyvat?locationIds=62585).

locations.title: Treasure Hoarder Diary
locations.description:
"Haha! This must be my lucky day, stumbling right into treasure just like that. Who would have thought that these ***squat little trees with red leaves*** would have so much treasure buried beneath them?"  

"But something's really weird about all this. Not a soul lives here, and I've never heard of anyone living here either. So, who buried this? And why are the trees with treasure buried under them so short, when all the other trees have grown normally?"  

"Well, whatever. Guess who's striking it rich this time? That's right, me, and no monster is going to stop me. But there's just so much treasure, I'll have to make some preparations. I'll bring a cart, and slowly dig the goods out from under those ***short, red-leaved trees***..."

locations.title: Notes with Missing Pages
locations.description:
"I have gone to Bubu Pharmacy to seek a cure for Jiang'er's troubled mind. I believe we should have the result in a few days..."

"Once I have finished my last mission, I will retire from the Millelith and move back home, away from this life of care and vigilance."

"I've given most of my life to the Millelith. If I want to enjoy life a bit now, I doubt the Ministry of Civil Affairs will deny me."

"If they don't, it's fine. I'll just take Jiang'er and leave Liyue for good. We'll live carefree lives somewhere else."

"Still, I am a Millelith for now, and I must serve until my final watch. Don't worry. Just take care of Jiang'er and wait for my return."

locations.title: Incomplete Register
locations.description:
The Incomplete Register can only be read after completing Sinister Instruction.

(A ragged register, seemingly an account used by the village chief.)

"Higi Village Residential Register:"

"...Torajirou, 13 years old, took ill and died. Shinji, 32 years old, took ill and died. Mitsuyo, 25 years old, took ill and died..."

"...Gin, 12 years old, took ill and died. Takaya, 55 years old, took ill and died. Nagabuchi, 42 years old, took ill and died. Eiri, 43 years old, took ill and died..."

"...The three Enoshita brothers, slain in battle. Kitada, 27 years old, on the run from the Shogunate. Fumiko, 36 years old, took ill and died. Shinko, 18 years old, lost at sea..."

"...Nameless Passerby A, sacrificed. Gongozaemon, 30 years old (?), sacrificed. Yamada, 23 years old, sacrificed..."

"...Senshiro, 4 years old, returned to oneness. Senshiro's Mother, around 25 years old, returned to oneness. Akiharu, 23 years old, summoned..."

"...The possessions of the aforementioned people shall be left here as a lure, all the better to provide living sacrifices for 'his' return..."

"...Chouji's Mother, around 32 years old (?), missing. 'He' is pleased with her, and thus she must be found..."

"...Nameless Outlander, seemingly young. About to take the bait..."
